hi,123dutch,
thank you very much for your books.

This book is amazing!!! I teach English as a second language, and I can assure you that this book will be taken into cosideration when I have to teach vocabulary.

Thanks a lot, 123dutch!!!

142 JPEG files.

Each file is a Scan of the open book and thus contains 2 pages of the book (one jpeg appears to be a photo, not a scan).

File Names are Generic Scan #s...so file names give no clue as to page number or contents of the pages themselves!

All Scans show center binding between pages which means slightly blurry and change in lightness/darkness.

Book details say 320 pages.  142 x 2 = 284 pages...so 36 pages are missing!

No Table of Contents
No Index
No Credits

All things mentioned, this is still a good book to DL...but this info should have mentioned in the Details.
Many thanks a excellent dictionary will be well used.
